This is a manual note, not a patch-package format.
Fix: @kabelsalat/web needs an exports map in package.json for ESM named exports to work.
Without it, Node.js resolves to the CJS bundle (.js) which loses named exports in ESM interop.

Fix applied at runtime in renderer.js setupScope() or manually:
  Add to node_modules/@kabelsalat/web/package.json:
  "exports": { ".": { "import": "./dist/index.mjs", "require": "./dist/index.js" } }
